divs: sighting detailsi bought a camera and was testing it out when i took these 3 photos and at the time i did not see anything with the naked eye! i live in ny and after 9\11 im very aware of what is in the sky. i saw no planes or copters or blimps or lights while taking these pictures. i did no use a flash and was just randomly shooting pictures and got 3 in a row of what appears to be a ball of light or reflecting light. the third pic is the actually shape of the object. i also had an encounter upstate i would like to include in the next submission.
Summary: Did not see it till after I took the pictures without a flash! then I noticed the ball of light and what looks like a blimp with no lights on.
